description:
NRFrequency: Table containing NR frequency configuration data for different cells.

- dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the data was recorded.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  An additional, likely redundant, identifier (always '1' in sample).
- Id4:  A combined identifier seemingly linking ARFCN and SCS.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier (always 'vsDataNRFrequency').
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (always 'EricssonSpecificAttributes').
- NRFrequency.smtcOffset:  SMTC (Synchronization Message Transmission Cycle) offset.
- NRFrequency.nRFrequencyId: Unique identifier for the NR frequency configuration.
- NRFrequency.smtcDuration: Duration of the SMTC.
- NRFrequency.smtcScs: Subcarrier spacing of the SMTC.
- NRFrequency.gscn: Global Cell ID.
- NRFrequency.arfcnValueNRDl: Absolute Radio Frequency Channel Number for Downlink.
- NRFrequency.reservedBy: Information on the entity that reserved the frequency.
- NRFrequency.bandList: List of NR bands used.
- NRFrequency.bandListManual: Manually configured list of NR bands.
- NRFrequency.smtcPeriodicity: Periodicity of the SMTC.
